- Likes: polished early‑80s AOR/new‑wave singles qualities — bright but economical synths, warm midrange guitars, ultra‑tight punchy bass/drums, glossy dry center‑front vocals with minimal reverb; narrow, focused imaging; tasteful multiband compression that gives vocal and rhythmic punch; crisp radio‑ready mastering that preserves clarity and presence. Also a retained liking for hook‑driven albums with warm midrange instruments, economical layering, clear instrument separation, rhythmic precision, concise 3–5‑minute songs, and useful packaging/liner notes.
